<div class="guide-page">
  <h1>Getting Started</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">
    From zero to a running agent swarm in five steps.
  </p>

  <div class="step-card">
    <div class="step-number">Step 1</div>
    <h2>Install Prerequisites</h2>
    <p>
      You need <strong>Ruby 3.4.5</strong>, <strong>Bundler</strong>, and <strong>SQLite3</strong> to run the Rails app.
      To use the agent swarm, you also need the <strong>Claude CLI</strong> and <strong>claude-swarm</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
      On macOS with Homebrew:
    </p>
    <pre><code>brew install rbenv ruby-build sqlite3
rbenv install 3.4.5
gem install bundler claude-swarm</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step-card">
    <div class="step-number">Step 2</div>
    <h2>Clone &amp; Install</h2>
    <p>
      Clone this repo and run the quickstart script. It checks your tools,
      installs gems, and prepares the database.
    </p>
    <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/CbiPerson/claude-on-rails-demo.git
cd claude-on-rails-demo
bin/quickstart</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step-card">
    <div class="step-number">Step 3</div>
    <h2>Start the Rails Server</h2>
    <p>
      Boot the app and open your browser to <code>http://localhost:3000</code>.
    </p>
    <pre><code>bin/rails server</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step-card">
    <div class="step-number">Step 4</div>
    <h2>Launch the Swarm</h2>
    <p>
      Open a <strong>second terminal</strong> (keep the server running) and start the agent swarm.
      The Architect agent will be ready for your instructions.
    </p>
    <pre><code>claude-swarm</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step-card">
    <div class="step-number">Step 5</div>
    <h2>Try a Prompt</h2>
    <p>
      Tell the swarm what to build. Start simple:
    </p>
    <pre><code>Add a Contact page with a name field, email field, and a submit button.</code></pre>
    <p>
      The Architect will delegate to the Controllers and Views agents.
      When it&rsquo;s done, refresh your browser to see the new page.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="guide-footer">
    For more detail, see the full
    <a href="https://github.com/CbiPerson/claude-on-rails-demo/blob/main/GETTING_STARTED.md">GETTING_STARTED.md</a>
    guide.
    &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;
    <a href="/examples">View example workflows &rarr;</a>
  </p>
</div>
